6fbd524","tid":2367663,"uid":76804,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T14:04:16.000Z","msg":"政府同武肺講掂數<br />\n唔會去21 23同25號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T14:05:55.000Z","msg":"對面街黎架⋯ <br />\n睇到好撚尷尬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T14:07:04.000Z","msg":"23 25號爆緊啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T15:44:46.000Z","msg":"爆到停唔到先封<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382ea34bd8c7660dfa9c7f41522a406cf121fb83","tid":2367663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T15:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5646ce4a9faab2bb9371f450de21fd078cfcc1","tid":2367663,"uid":303554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T16:14:16.000Z","msg":"次次都話冇資料，幾時搵Constance 出黎答下問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1007822a78b940e3bcd4f76e695a9884c8ec7bf","tid":2367663,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T18:30:49.000Z","msg":"210115 每日監察衞生署強制檢測名單有冇出錯 [附: 佐敦西北社區強制檢測]<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gzzFNT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gzzFNT</a>"},{"pid":"2b8ed8c5be66fd8d161fbbf17d1dff50a5575042","tid":2367663,"uid":51754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15719dc7e01cef5415c2b0214c274dcd652a6821","tid":2367663,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T14:05:00.000Z","msg":"衞生署署長發出隔離令<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  政府發言人表示，衞生署署長林秉恩醫生昨日（五月一日）向灣仔維景酒店發出隔離令，以防止人類豬流感（甲型流感Ｈ１Ｎ１）擴散。<br />\n<br />\n  由於香港首宗人類豬流感確診個案涉及的一名二十五歲墨西哥藉男子於四月三十日從墨西哥經上海抵港後入住該酒店，衞生署署長遂發出隔離令。<br />\n<br />\n  衞生署署長是根據香港法例第５９９章《預防及控制疾病條例》第２５條賦予的權力發出隔離令，以保障整個社會的健康。<br />\n<br />\n  <span class=\"red\">隔離令要求酒店的員工和住客不可離開該酒店</span>，部分人士會於今日（五月二日）遷入用作為隔離中心的麥理浩夫人度假村。他們將會被隔離七日。<br />\n<br />\n  衞生署衞生防護中心醫護人員為逗留在酒店人士進行身體檢查，出現流感病徵的人士會被送往醫院接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n  食物環境衞生署員工會為酒店進行徹底清潔及消毒。<br />\n <br />\n  發言人說：「我們理解今次的隔離措施對酒店住客造成不便。由於情況特殊，不得不採取這非常措施，我們希望住客能體諒和支持，和整體社會共同對抗這次疫症。」<br />\n<br />\n  此外，衞生防護中心已開始追蹤有機會與該名病人接觸的人士。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人籲請曾於四月二十九日乘坐墨西哥航空公司（航班號碼ＡＭ９８）從墨西哥蒂華納飛往上海，或四月三十日乘坐東方航空公司（航班號碼ＭＵ５０５）從上海抵港人士，或同日入住維景酒店並已離開的人士，致電衞生防護中心熱線２１２５ １１１１，以便衞生當局立即進行調查。<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>２００９年５月２日（星期六）</strong></span><br />\n香港時間２時１８分<br />\n<br />\n以前都出過<br />\n即係封咗成棟嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T18:32:06.000Z","msg":"隔離七日情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25098caf5d580a417d7b44e117e239759cb1e66","tid":2367663,"uid":37136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T18:42:28.000Z","msg":"【 2021年恐怖份子最新打飛機片「守城」 】 上線啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nm35Ra4T3_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNm35Ra4T3_8&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=14f41f32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nm35Ra4T3_8</a><br />\n各位手足識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}